stories.text:
Imagine that you suddenly got unlimited time and money, and could design the programming language of your dreams, without any compromises, what would the main features of your language be?

You can pick and choose features from existing languages, create entirely new features, real or fictional ones even, that we might not even be able to actually construct today!
